"Blue Moon Cinnamon Horchata brewed by Coors Brewing Company, with an ABV of 5.50%  This brew pours out a nice amber color with a nice white head. Cinnamon Horchata is a unfiltered brew, this brew has cloudy tent to it.  The smell is rich with cinnamon and sweetness.  You also pick up a hit of gains in the smell of this brew. Now for the taste, it is rich with cinnamon and spices.  This brew taste like apple pie, not saying that is a bad thing.  There is nothing overpowering in this brew, it has a nice balance to it. The mouthfeel is great with spices and smoothness.  Coors Brewing Company did a nice job with brew. I would buy this brew again. Overall I',m giving this brew a 4.5 out of 5."
